com.dec.avw.core.TaskFunction.name: folder_settings
com.dec.avw.core.TaskFunction.description:
This function will open a dialog to manipulate the folder settings of the top-level DMS folder of the process instance on which this function is applied.
Normally editing those settings can also be achived via toolbar action 'Folder properties' in the 'Documents' tab of that instance, but if that action is not available there it can be provided by adding this taskfunction to the process instance (e.g. in the process history)
